{"tid":2379050,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"佐敦夜後如死城鼠屍遍地","createTime":"2021-01-25T03:26:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T03:30:17.000Z","uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d6afdce0e6c20bfdab8e6d300f466b4f6b09716a","tid":2379050,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:26:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jXOBLSP2_g5cUZMYLNO.1w--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NC44/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/mPfpOfiY_dtiKkxEKFHYmw--~B/aD00Mjg7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/thesun.hk.com/0f1940645cb2c76d74e425ef8108ef9f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FjXOBLSP2_g5cUZMYLNO.1w--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NC44%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FmPfpOfiY_dtiKkxEKFHYmw--~B%2FaD00Mjg7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fthesun.hk.com%2F0f1940645cb2c76d74e425ef8108ef9f&h=a2f37eb9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】佐敦昨日成為指定「受限區域」，期間非指定人士不得進出，「禁足」的首個晚上，該區域一帶猶如死城，除了有小量市民陸續登記進行檢測外，街道上僅見穿着保護衣的工作人員以及駐守封鎖線的警員，場面冷清。有居民批評區內衞生情況欠佳，記者區域外、廣東道流動檢疫站附近發現死老鼠，恐新冠肺炎未平，又爆鼠疫。<br />\n<br />\n3官方支援熱線2失效<br />\n<br />\n佐敦封鎖的區域一帶受到嚴密監管，有關人士除了於指定時間到指定的檢測地點，進行新冠肺炎病毒測試外，其餘時間一律不可擅離居所。區內居民須戴上白色手帶，駐守的工作人員若發現有居民於街上亂逛，會立即勸喻返回居所。據了解，當局將大廈劃分成不同區域，配以指定時間進行檢測，每個檢測位置與居民所住大廈距離非常接近，一般約20至30米路程，避免居民於區內流連。政府為受檢人士提供3條支援熱線，惟昨晚記者實測後，其中一條熱線未能接通，另一條則無人接聽。<br />\n<br />\n對於佐敦一帶有居民批評區內衞生情況欠佳，記者昨日於封鎖區外、廣東道流動檢疫站附近發現死老鼠，清潔工人到場用紙將鼠屍包起，扔入垃圾收集車後送走。現場所見，垃圾箱堆滿垃圾，但未有工作人員處理，有惹鼠患之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WNVBT5H2JW4qr1PSSctJVg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NC44/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/V14lBQ5Lh5vIJIXgEAD9Aw--~B/aD00Mjg7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/thesun.hk.com/e4bd9279e3624e4374edb6bd3699d22e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWNVBT5H2JW4qr1PSSctJVg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY4NC44%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FV14lBQ5Lh5vIJIXgEAD9Aw--~B%2FaD00Mjg7dz02MDA7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fko%2Fthesun.hk.com%2Fe4bd9279e3624e4374edb6bd3699d22e&h=f5b0502b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6b69229d156e683b44bdfe52d5eb7e1c1ea91865","tid":2379050,"uid":183758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T03:30:17.000Z","msg":"連老鼠都頂唔緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}